Close active window -> Super+Q
Kill hyprland  -> Super+Delete
Toggle window floating -> Super+W
Toggle fullscreen -> Alt+Return
Start hyprlock -> Super+L
Show logout/power menu -> Super+Backspace
Launch terminal -> Super+T
Launch file manager -> Super+E
Launch text editor -> Super+C
Launch web browser -> Super+F
Launch system monitor -> Ctrl+Shift+Escape
Launch color picker -> Super+Shift+P
Take a screenshot -> Super+P
Show app drawer -> Super+A
Show window switcher -> Super+Tab
Previous song/media -> Super+Ctrl+0
Next song/media -> Super+Ctrl+=
Play/pause song/media -> Super+Ctrl+-
Move window focus up -> Super+I
Move window focus down -> Super+K
Move window focus left  -> Super+J
Move window focus right -> Super+L
Focus prevous monitor  -> Super+Ctrl+1
Focus next monitor  -> Super+Ctrl+2
Move to prevous workspace -> Super+1
Move to next workspace  -> Super+2
Move to prevous workspace (scroll) -> Super+mouse_down
Move to next workspace (scroll) -> Super+mouse_up
Move focused window to prevous workspace -> Super+Shift+1
Move focused window to next workspace -> Super+Shift+2
Move focused window to prevous workspace silently -> Super+Alt+1
Move focused window to next workspace silently  -> Super+Alt+2
Move window (mouse)  -> Super+mouse:272
Resize window (mouse) -> Super+mouse:273
Move window (keyboard) -> Super+Z
Resize window (keyboard)  -> Super+X
Toggle window split direction -> Super+J
